description:
Element clients probe these on login/lifecycle. Returning 404 mostly works but causes noisy errors and disables features.

- GET /_matrix/client/v3/capabilities → { capabilities: { 'm.change_password': { enabled: true }, 'm.room_versions': { default: '11', available: { '11': 'stable' } } } }
- GET /_matrix/client/v3/voip/turnServer → empty list is valid: { 'username': '', 'password': '', 'uris': [], 'ttl': 86400 }
- POST /_matrix/client/v3/user/{userId}/openid/request_token → mint a short-lived OpenID token bound to the user

All small. Group into one commit.
